Abertis’s Saba Unit Valued at 1 Billion Euros, Expansion Says

-- B y   S h a r o n   S m y t h
-- 
2011-04-08T05:24:32Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-08/abertis-s-saba-unit-valued-at-1-billion-euros-expansion-says.html
Abertis Infraestructuras SA (ABE)  hired AZ
Capital to advise it on the sale of its Saba Infraestructuras
parking and logistics unit,  Expansion  reported, citing
unidentified people familiar with the matter.  Saba is valued at 1 billion euros ($1.4 billion) and the
sale may take place before Abertis holds its  shareholders’
meeting  in June, the newspaper added.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Sharon Smyth in  Madrid  at 
 ssmyth2@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew Blackman at   ablackman@bloomberg.net . 